quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  18,35,"Wadakhala jannatahu wahuwa thalimunlinafsihi qala ma athunnu an tabeedahathihi abada"
  18,36,"Wama athunnu assaAAataqa-imatan wala-in rudidtu ila rabbee laajidannakhayran minha munqalaba"
  18,37,"Qala lahu sahibuhu wahuwa yuhawiruhuakafarta billathee khalaqaka min turabinthumma min nutfatin thumma sawwaka rajula"
  18,38,"Lakinna huwa Allahu rabbee walaoshriku birabbee ahada"
  18,39,"Walawla ith dakhalta jannatakaqulta ma shaa Allahu la quwwata illabillahi in tarani ana aqalla minka malanwawalada"
  18,40,"FaAAasa rabbee an yu/tiyani khayranmin jannatika wayursila AAalayha husbananmina assama-i fatusbiha saAAeedanzalaqa"
  18,41,"Aw yusbiha maohaghawran falan tastateeAAa lahu talaba"
  18,42,"Waoheeta bithamarihi faasbahayuqallibu kaffayhi AAala ma anfaqa feehawahiya khawiyatun AAala AAurooshihawayaqoolu ya laytanee lam oshrik birabbee ahada"
  18,43,"Walam takun lahu fi-atun yansuroonahumin dooni Allahi wama kana muntasira"
  18,44,"Hunalika alwalayatu lillahialhaqqi huwa khayrun thawaban wakhayrun AAuqba"
  18,45,"Wadrib lahum mathala alhayatiaddunya kama-in anzalnahu mina assama-ifakhtalata bihi nabatu al-ardi faasbahahasheeman tathroohu arriyahu wakanaAllahu AAala kulli shay-in muqtadira"
